tion></section></section></section><section><br/></section><section><br/></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">①关注【绘栈】服务号</span></section><section><img class=\"rich_pages \" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/iagv8to0KtudFAwlh0ZBSfUxXRy5jpYUrE55g04ZDQ3bVVLnkvibPmicKAFS3dE7T0FS8Q9y0gBVCW9C3l1W4F3TA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\"/></section><section><br/></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">②进入“社群课程”——“小鹅通”</span></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">③进入“手绘打卡”——“我爱铅笔画彩铅每周一画”</span></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">④开启“打卡通知”，可及时收到作业提醒</span></section><section><br/></section><section><img class=\"rich_pages \" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/iagv8to0Ktuc3AeWG8n9yRB64n4KrPgQM2ke1WKyFeicVkjpyQAey4wlia2IwKbROmntdBGturkao9hibDLmUGJEmQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\"/></section><section><br/></section><section><br/></section><section><br/></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">加入彩铅学习交流群</span><br/></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">备注：彩铅打卡入群</span></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">（拒绝纯微商，长得好看也不行）</span></section><section><img class=\"rich_pages \" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/iagv8to0KtufhoaQ5AlDUpxMm6Xh85TuicdnXlenVa9mR2oWYeQMDzMjIxvTU7liaJMfAEMHkzo7mu2vQIeUCYkRw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\"/></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10px;\">木头是我<br/></span></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10px;\">铅笔君是我</span></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10px;\">绘栈和我爱铅笔画里的铅笔君</span></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 10px;\">都是我</span></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','零基础小伙伴怎么看图文教程学习？\n①老师说要叠色三层的，大家不要偷懒，一层也不能少；\n②学会看素材，老师不是凭空想象画画的，大家不能完全跟着老师的步骤描画，去看看老师这步为什么这么画；\n③明暗关系很重要，基本的素描知识大家要补起来；\n④画画过程中站起来很重要，放松颈椎，及时调整画面。\n⑤耐心很重要，画彩铅就是一个慢慢的过程，想看到自己的作品一点点像变魔术一样变得好看，就要在这个过程里怀着最美好的期待。\n\n彩铅工具怎么选择？\n彩铅：彩铅有基础的，高阶的，效果和价格成正比。选择合适自己的，不论什么彩铅，买回来记得做一份色卡，因为不管是跟教程还是跟老师的课，不可能买齐所有品牌彩铅，我们对照色卡找相似颜色就行。\n画纸：画彩铅有个公认的道理，画纸比彩铅更重要，好的画纸能更好的表现彩铅的性能，更容易上色，能叠更多层颜色。\n\n彩铅工具怎么保管：\n是工具都需要好好保管，有同学说水溶彩铅不好，容易受潮，油性彩铅保管不好同样会受潮。\n如果你是在比较潮湿的地方，记得停手即收工具，纸和笔都是。\n彩铅不管是铁盒还是布艺笔帘，都请在外面加护一层密封袋；\n没有画完的纸张，请放置在密封袋中保存。\n家里零食里的干燥剂可以留好，每个密封袋里放置。网上买也非常便宜。',NULL,0,'2020-06-02 11:23:59','1260223757249355776',NULL,'1267481346869760000,1267481382982717440,1267481989126754304,1267482618456903680','1267488059324829696,1267488112818982912,1267488196713451520,1267488382747611136',NULL),
